4.找到人性关键点，一攻即破

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appzazEaBy34184/a_5cdb900ddf837_FGR1ZpiI

<section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em;"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 190px; height: 40px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzazEaBy34184/image/ueditor/50239600_1544079300.png&#39;); background-size: contain; background-attachment: scroll; box-sizing: border-box; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 8px 0px 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">专栏介绍</strong></p><p><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">战国时代，诸子蜂起，百家争鸣，各种思想学说竞相出现，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这个时期，就是人们常说的中华文明“轴心时代”。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">或许你知道孙膑、庞涓、苏秦、张仪，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">但你是否了解，这些战国时期呼风唤雨的人物背后，都有着一位共同的老师，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这位老师是中国历史上极富神秘色彩的传奇人物，诸子百家中纵横家的鼻祖。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">史书中说他是长短纵横的谋略家；传奇中说他是神通广大的智者；</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">宗教故事中说他是未卜先知的神仙；民间流传中说他是预测吉凶的命相家；</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">在文化史上，他更是与孔子、孟子、庄子等先哲齐名的学术大家。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">美国前国务卿基辛格，日本著名企业家大桥武夫，德国著名历史学家斯宾格勒，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">都曾拜读他的智慧，对他推崇备至，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">他被称为“中国历史上最被低估的圣人”，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这个人，就是传奇的鬼谷子。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如果说，儒家解决的是人与人的关系，道家解决的是人与规律的关系，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">那么，鬼谷子的纵横之术就是让你建功立业、真正充满权谋策略的智慧。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">《鬼谷子：五分钟抓住人性弱点》课程，去繁化简，用22讲，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为你提炼拿来就用的鬼谷子智慧，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">给你一套运筹帷幄的计谋宝典、决胜千里的实用指南。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你会学到在职场竞争中巧打心理战，做到防守滴水不漏，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">掌握人性，抓住对手弱点，攻击见缝插针，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">知己知彼、欲擒故纵、做到鱼与熊掌兼得，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你会得到一剂自我修炼自我提升的催化剂，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你的意志会变得更坚定，你会习得深藏不露识时务的能力，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你会掌握揣摩心理说服对方的技巧，你会拥有慧眼识人的本领，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">潜移默化的提升你的见识与境界，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">助你在职场上、生活中，</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">开创新局、扭转乾坤，做自己人生的掌舵师。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 190px; height: 40px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzazEaBy34184/image/ueditor/93324400_1544079354.png&#39;); background-size: contain; background-attachment: scroll; box-sizing: border-box; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 8px 0px 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">在职场碰壁、被对手打压到“翻身无门”的你</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">总被对手利用、屡屡吃“哑巴亏”的你</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">看不透对方，被自己信任的人“背后一刀”伤害的你</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">自我控制力差、常常突然“情绪失控”的你</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">努力工作，在领导眼中却比不过那些“马屁精”的你</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; backgro